Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.12,0:01:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分開了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.25,0:01:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為邪惡帝皇多惡達\N支配了這座山的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連彩虹的顏色也變成了黑白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.10,0:01:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、火美子和武一郎師傅\N一邊與多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.91,0:01:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於上了第三界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.22,0:01:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本第三界層是由\N支配寒冷的極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.55,0:01:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和支配炎熱的灼熱之盾\N令這世界的氣溫剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.80,0:02:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是多惡達用灼熱之劍\N換了極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令第三界層變成了一個\N熱得不得了的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.14,0:02:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了令這世界恢復原來氣溫\N便一定要找到極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為了找極寒之劍\N和師傅他們分開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.14,0:02:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人來到了第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.22,0:02:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏火龍告訴我\N要到野野谷去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十六話\N悲戀,極光傳說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.90,0:02:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我技術不錯吧\N嗨,野野谷還有很遠嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.33,0:02:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.57,0:02:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像很沒精神呢\N好,在到達之前玩接尾句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.90,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接尾句（接屁股）?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.26,0:03:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在想什麼?\N只要用詞語來玩遊戲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.58,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不懂嗎?算了\N那休息一下吧,有點累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.72,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊\N不快點找到極寒之劍不行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是\N但是只是休息一會可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.37,0:03:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而令人更冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這處真是個陰森可怕的地方\N渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.62,0:03:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這座山是連村內的人\N也未去過的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.04,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說這裏是非常神聖的地方\N進入這裏的人都會中邪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.89,0:03:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真…真是的\N你想用那些話來嚇我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我突然變得精神了\N不如出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.20,0:04:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極光?這便是極光嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有照相機便好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是已看慣了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種色的極光是第一次見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?是霧嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼也看不見呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.73,0:04:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,玩那個吧\N叫接尾句的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊,那麼,首先是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.20,0:04:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪(YUKII)的KI\N你要說出用KI開頭的詞語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.50,0:04:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KI嗎?那麼…啄木鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.00,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狐貍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是KI嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.60,0:04:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KI,KI,KI…\N不要催我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,前面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你抓緊我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,它追來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蛋,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.49,0:05:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙太冷冬眠了嗎?\N起來啊!小蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真難纏的傢伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,再快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了,已不能再加快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你想對我們怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.59,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算要吃的話\N我們也完全不好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.92,0:06:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,竟當我是傻瓜\N我已生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!去吧!小蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫你上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你啊!快離開雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蛋,噴火吧,去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.94,0:07:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?你不是百人僊人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼會在這裏?\N而且變得很細小呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.30,0:07:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識百人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是在第三界層見過面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.51,0:07:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三界層?那便是真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.71,0:07:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是千人僊人\N是百人僊人的哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?所以才這麼像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.81,0:08:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它叫西蒙\N是守護我的善良生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?原來是這樣\N嚇了我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.72,0:08:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要摸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.98,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西蒙是神聖的生物\N隨便碰的會受到天罰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.98,0:08:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.77,0:08:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是西蒙\N這附近一帶也是在守護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以便沒有人敢接近這裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千人僊人\N請問野野谷在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏便是野野谷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.38,0:08:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?那麼這裏會有\N極寒之劍的線索吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.40,0:08:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,快點去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪,沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是剛才扭傷了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.52,0:08:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能走到這裏\N應該沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼你從剛才起\N便一直在忍著嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從火美子那拿了萬能藥來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,塗點藥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.40,0:09:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說救世主在創界山出現了\N難道是這個少年?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好\N這藥的效力令人難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟敢這個樣子回來\N你知不知醜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.55,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這次一定會令渡知道\N什麼是無用的反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.43,0:09:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,但這次再失敗的話\N別忘了你將失去翻身之地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這次會打起精神作戰的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.26,0:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行呢\N完全沒有像樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?千人僊人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.38,0:10:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道呢\N好吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,不可以摸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!千人僊人去了哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說些話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒理由能答我吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.56,0:10:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.13,0:10:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.33,0:10:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪,它不是想嚇我\N而是想和我玩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,不要啊,我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不會和人親近的西蒙也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那少年果然是真正的救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.02,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千人僊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.80,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,我告訴你\N有關亞撒姆和胡娜拉的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞撒姆和胡娜拉的傳說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千人僊人,這裏是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.41,0:11:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很遙遠的昔日,神的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看,那棵很大的樹下有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他便是亞撒姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞撒姆原來是秋天和冬天的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.71,0:11:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而春天和夏天的神\N是位叫胡娜拉的女神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.53,0:12:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們二人犯了一個\N不能回頭的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.00,0:12:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相愛的人永不分離\N也許是很自然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.20,0:12:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是秋天和冬天的神\N與春天和夏天的神在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便會令季節轉換消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.40,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,他們相愛\N本來便是不容許的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算因他們的關係\N令其他人受苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也絕不分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.23,0:12:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此時愛的女神處罰了他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受心替之矢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.70,0:12:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉變成了石像\N被困到了第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.80,0:12:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內心被抽空的亞撒姆很傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.00,0:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為太傷心的關係\N令亞撒姆也變成了石像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可憐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛之女神也是這樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.76,0:13:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以便只容許他們\N一千年相聚一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每一千年,亞撒姆像\N都會架起一道光之橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.51,0:13:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在直通往第四界層的那道光\N亞撒姆和胡娜拉便重聚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.30,0:13:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個便是亞撒姆和胡娜拉的傳說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極寒之劍便在胡娜拉像手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼胡娜拉像在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.41,0:13:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡娜拉像\N為了追尋亞撒姆像的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.95,0:13:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第四界層中四處遊走不定\N沒有人知道她在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.88,0:13:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是千年一度之日快來到了\N那個極光便是先兆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.80,0:14:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快亞撒姆和胡娜拉便相聚\N也許那時便是機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你不要有事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,洞穴內比較涼快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡就像是我兒子一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.96,0:14:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一人在踏上危險的旅程時\N在下享樂是武士之恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,你原來是渡的父親?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.05,0:14:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,和你說話令我很累\N你走開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也來祈求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.06,0:14:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以抱著玩的心情啊\N要誠心誠意地祈求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣渡才能安然回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.59,0:14:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一群大好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.58,0:15:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,誰也不明白我的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殘酷大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在怕什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.03,0:15:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣的傢伙\N還可以迷惘嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎,古拿瑪\N再次失敗是不可饒恕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.25,0:15:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真失敗的話…\N你便沒有命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生,你回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…\N我發現了有好東西吃的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要一起來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.06,0:15:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.54,0:15:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下擔心渡,沒有食慾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏啊?\N在這屋內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.44,0:15:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要第一\N是在下先啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師! 什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.41,0:15:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪的傢伙,好了,去吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.29,0:16:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?沒有食物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,有點不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘩!是"巴BQ"啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,斬不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!古拿瑪,來幫手啊\N喂!古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.07,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!\N難道古拿瑪那傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.20,0:16:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,你竟敢瞞騙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.69,0:17:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼千人僊人,我們出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.76,0:17:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向那極光前進\N一定會有些什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.60,0:17:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是呢,呆在這裏想的話\N什麼也找不到,你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是東傑何狄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還記得\N總算不是無用的反抗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為你已引退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳,竟敢這樣說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了,那些冰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流下來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你便明白\N什麼是無用的反抗了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.94,0:18:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在做無用的反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.04,0:18:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的反抗不是無用的\N去吧!西蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.48,0:18:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,已不可饒恕了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.02,0:18:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣便用魔神決勝負吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妙多龍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.40,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[妙多龍]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.94,0:18:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不會讓你們逃出這個山谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,西蒙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無用的反抗!無用的反抗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西蒙!\N好了,最後一擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.51,0:19:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險!奇怪珠攻擊!去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!是機會了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.94,0:19:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.13,0:20:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳!可惡的龍神丸\N今天一定要和你做個了斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.40,0:20:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的龍神丸\N我要把你打得稀爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.47,0:20:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是無用的反抗呢,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我令你死得痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.00,0:20:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.10,0:20:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又再阻礙我了\N那麼我先收拾你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這是什麼傢伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擲回去吧!龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.76,0:21:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.57,0:21:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是無用的反抗啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.01,0:21:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西蒙一定可以幫到你們\N帶它去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.40,0:21:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,千人僊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,出發吧,西蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一路小心了!

